; v18 Core Smoke Test
; Purpose: verify basic v18 PRINT/INPUT/WAIT still work on V24Pure profile.
; Expected output (first screen):
;   === V18 CORE SMOKE ===
;   PASS: PRINTL works
;   PASS: PRINT works
;   PASS: PRINTFORM works 123
;   PASS: PRINTFORML works 456
;   [WAIT prompt]

@EVENTFIRST
PRINTL === V18 CORE SMOKE ===
PRINTL PASS: PRINTL works
PRINT PASS: PRINT works
PRINTL
LOCAL = 123
PRINTFORML PASS: PRINTFORM works {LOCAL}
LOCAL:1 = 456
PRINTFORML PASS: PRINTFORML works {LOCAL:1}
WAIT
RETURN 0
